OL,7,FThe water industry regulator Ofwat is
OL,8,Fseeking new powers from the Government
OL,9,Fto clamp down on billions in cash
OL,10,Fpayouts to investors as it seeks to
OL,11,Fforce greater investment into
OL,12,Fenvironment improvements, i can reveal.
OL,14,FIt is understood that one outcome of
OL,15,FOfwat's review of the industry that
OL,16,Fbegan last summer is that it will seek
OL,17,Fnew controls to limit excessive
OL,18,Fdividends paid to investors by
OL,19,FEngland's nine water and sewage
OL,20,Fcompanies.
OL,3,COfwat seeks new powers to force water
OL,4,Ccompanies to clean up rivers by
OL,5,Cblocking investor payouts
